      <p>These bottom-dwelling sea creatures are dangerous only to their prey. If disturbed, they usually try to escape.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2302912"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
